data.description: Step into this stunning custom home, just a short jaunt from FW & Weatherford! Unleash your inner chef in the dream kitchen with a commercial-grade gas range, dual sinks, twin islands, a stainless steel refrigerator fit for the pros, & a walk-in pantry that's practically a secret passage. Family rm boasts 16ft ceilings adorned with beams. Discover not 1, but 2 offices– oval oasis downstairs & private workspace upstairs. The master suite is a sanctuary with a cozy sitting area, bathroom that's a work of art, closet designed for royalty, & even its own laundry nook. The 1st floor also hosts a guest suite & 2 charming bdrms, each with its own laundry haven. Entertain like never before in the oversized game room & bar, or unwind in the media room. The patio beckons with a seating area, a fireplace to cozy up to, & a bar for those who appreciate the finer things. As if that weren't enough, there's a spacious 40x70 shop complete with a 4 stall barn–because your dreams deserve room to roam!
